originContent: ## About
TextMeshPro dynamic font assets have a very annoying habit of saving their dynamically generated binary data in the
translatedContent: TextMeshPro 动态字体资源有一个非常恼人的习惯，就是将其动态生成的二进制数据保存在

originContent: same text file as their configuration data. This causes massive headaches for version control.
translatedContent: 与其配置数据相同的文本文件中。这给版本控制带来了极大的麻烦。

originContent: The script from this package addresses the above issue. It runs whenever any assets in the project are about to be saved. If any of
translatedContent: 本包中的脚本解决了上述问题。它在项目中任何资源即将保存时运行。如果这些

originContent: those assets are a TMP dynamic font asset, they will have their dynamically generated data cleared before they are
translatedContent: 资源是 TMP 动态字体资源，它们的动态生成数据将在保存前被清除，从而防止这些数据污染版本控制。

originContent: saved, which prevents that data from ever polluting the version control.

translatedContent: 感谢 @cxode 提出的这个精彩解决方案：

originContent: Credits to @cxode which came up with this brilliant solution:
`https://forum.unity.com/threads/tmpro-dynamic-font-asset-constantly-changes-in-source-control.1227831/#post-8934711`

translatedContent: 我的贡献是将脚本制作成一个兼容 upm 的包，便于安装。

originContent: My contribution is making script into a upm compatible package that could be easily installed.
translatedContent: 对性能进行了改进，并增加了对边缘情况的额外检查。

originContent: Some performance improvements and additional checks were made for edge cases.
translatedContent: 此外，我创建了一个测试，用于快速检测脚本在您的项目/Unity 版本中是否正常工作。

originContent: Also, I created a test to quickly test whether script is working properly in your project/unity version.
## Installation
translatedContent: 通过 git URL 安装：

originContent: Install via git URL:
`https://github.com/STARasGAMES/tmpro-dynamic-data-cleaner.git#upm`

translatedContent: 或者通过在您的 **`manifest.json`** 中添加新条目安装。

originContent: Or by adding a new entry in your **`manifest.json`**.
```json
"dependencies": {
"com.starasgames.tmpro-dynamic-data-cleaner": "https://github.com/STARasGAMES/tmpro-dynamic-data-cleaner.git#upm",
"testables" : ["com.starasgames.tmpro-dynamic-data-cleaner"]
To make integration test visible in the TestRunner window you need to add the `"testables"` attribute, but this is optinal.
translatedContent: 要使集成测试在 TestRunner 窗口中可见，您需要添加 `"testables"` 属性，但这是可选的。
